title: Maker Hikoushiki Hatsune Mix
original_name: メーカー非公式 初音みっくす
sinopse: A manga based on Yamaha's voice synthesizer VOCALOID and it's mascots, mainly Miku Hatsune. This character is the first heroine who has had a worldwide hit from the Vocaloid Character Voice Series. Every new chapter has a different Miku, showing different aspects of the world of music!
